review_text: If you want top level service from a community bank then look no further. The staff is amazing, experienced, friendly and always willing to go the extra mile, even without being asked. Great mortgage department for residential and commercial loans.
Great bank, wonderful & helpful staff. Very happy I chose Dime Bank for my banking needs
Young and vibrant staff.  Perfect bank for modern banking services.
All of my banking needs are met at this bank by really nice bank employees!
